---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section id="about" title="About">
  <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
    <p>
      I've spent the past three years as a backend and platform engineer at Amazon, on the
      AWS Security data platform team, building ingestion pipelines that process
      <strong class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">11+ PB/day</strong>
      of security telemetry. I owned a multi-cluster ingestion feature that saved
      <strong class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">$1.4M/year</strong>
      in infrastructure and cut weekly Sev-2 incidents from around sixty down to two. I also
      designed a streaming API ingestion service that replaced a brittle Lambda-based
      pipeline and saved another $100K/year.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before Amazon I did AI research with MIT, Cal State, and Kean University, and
      freelanced full-stack work through college. I graduated Magna Cum Laude in CS.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm based in Austin, TX. Right now I'm building side projects — like
      <a href="#projects" class="font-medium text-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--accent-strong)]">JobPing</a>,
      the service powering my own job search — and looking for my next role.
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>
